<body>

  <h1>ğŸ“˜ Learn About Plural Nouns</h1>

  <div class="box">
    <h2>ğŸ“– Grammar Explanation</h2>
    <p>A <strong>singular noun</strong> names one person, place, or thing. <span class="example">Example: box, home</span></p>
